ity of Godhead, seated beside the individual soul, is the witness of the individual soul’s activities and is the source of the soul’s various types of consciousness. The Supersoul gives the individual soul an opportunity "])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"to act freely and witnesses his activities. The functions of all these different manifestations of the Supreme Lord automatically become clarified for the pure Kṛṣṇa conscious devotee engaged in transcendental service to the Lord. The gigantic universal form of the Lord called \u003cem\u003eadhidaivata\u003c/em\u003e is contemplated by the neophyte who cannot approach the Supreme Lord in His manifestation as Supersoul. The neophyte is advised to contemplate the universal form, or \u003cem\u003evirāṭ-puruṣa,\u003c/em\u003e whose legs are considered the lower planets, whose eyes are considered the sun and moon, and whose head is considered the upper planetary system.55:[\"$\",\"div\",\"2376-purport,2376-purport\",{\"className\":\"av-purport\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-center em:leading-5 em:text-xl font-bold em:mb-4\",\"children\":\"Purport\"}],[[\"$\",\"$L41\",\"child-2381\",{\"child\":\"$2b:props:children:0:props:children:props:page:child_items:0:children:3:child_items:4:children:0\",\"hasId\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"em:mb-4 em:leading-8 em:text-base s-justify\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$d1\"}}]}]]]}]\n56:[\"$\",\"div\",\"2382-devanagari,2382-devanagari\",{\"className\":\"av-devanagari\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-center em:leading-5 em:text-xl font-bold em:mb-4 hidden\",\"children\":\"Devanagari\"}],[[\"$\",\"$L41\",\"child-2383\",{\"child\":\"$2b:props:children:0:props:children:props:page:child_items:0:children:4:child_items:0:children:0\",\"hasId\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"em:mb-4 em:leading-8 em:text-lg text-center\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"अन्तकाले च म